Datos.Descripcion: Clint Barton, or Hawkeye, is a master archer with exceptional accuracy and a wide range of specialized arrows. His skills and bravery make him a crucial member of the Avengers. Although he lacks superpowers, his precision and expertise in archery make him a standout hero.

Once a brilliant but arrogant neurosurgeon, Stephen Strange's life changed forever after a car accident robbed him of the use of his hands. Searching for healing, he discovered the hidden world of magic and alternate dimensions, becoming the Sorcerer Supreme and the protector of Earth against mystical threats.

Clint Barton, or Hawkeye, is a master archer with exceptional accuracy and a wide range of specialized arrows. His skills and bravery make him a crucial member of the Avengers. Although he lacks superpowers, his precision and expertise in archery make him a standout hero.
